				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$dW\, = \frac{{n_1 }}{{s\,l}}\sigma \,l = \frac{{n_1 }}{s}\sigma $$\end{document}

If there are n2 particles in bunch 2, the number of interactions that will be observed is\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
